Class SimpleItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.theprogramsrc.supercoreapi.spigot.items.SimpleItem

  • public class SimpleItem
extends java.lang.Object
    SimpleItem is a representation of a ItemStack with more options in one class.
